      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777999185261,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Enities\n\n- Original URLs\n- Short URLs\n- Users",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Enities\n\n- Original URLs\n- Short URLs\n- Users",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FAaOmlh23zG0cqgHntniJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1594.135706585709,
      "y": 743.5927528221301,
      "width": 765.0994873046875,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ae",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1189458674,
      "version": 428,
      "versionNonce": 2105692082,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777999482965,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "APIs\n\nNOTE: Derive the APIs from the functional Requirements, Always. 1-1 mapping.\n\n1. Shortern a URL:\nPOST /url -> shortUrl\n{\n    originalUrl,\n    alias?,\n    expirationTime?\n}\n\n2. Redirection of an url:\nGET (shortUrl) -> Redirect to OriginalUrl",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "APIs\n\nNOTE: Derive the APIs from the functional Requirements, Always. 1-1 mapping.\n\n1. Shortern a URL:\nPOST /url -> shortUrl\n{\n    originalUrl,\n    alias?,\n    expirationTime?\n}\n\n2. Redirection of an url:\nGET (shortUrl) -> Redirect to OriginalUrl",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
