    },
    {
      "id": "WwuztPFvW-xKHkxevdFXo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 617.9600763844842,
      "y": 1940.5168808388319,
      "width": 477.4997253417969,
      "height": 500,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "at",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1517477554,
      "version": 725,
      "versionNonce": 1336321266,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778000527559,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Options for Redirection ?\n1. 302 Redirect:\n    -> A Temporary Redirect. \n    Browsers won't cache it, so it needs our \n    service every single time.\n    -> Good for Analystic in server and make \n    sure that the server works, as it hots server\n    everytime.\n\nSince we dont care about Analystics,\n302 makes more sense here...\n\n2. 301 Redirect:\n    -> A Permanent Redirect. Browser \n    knows where to redirect, and it won't\n    need our service anymore.\n    -> Good, if want to save the overhead\n    compute of lookingup the long url for \n    the short one.\n    -> Efficient but one-time use-case only !",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Options for Redirection ?\n1. 302 Redirect:\n    -> A Temporary Redirect. \n    Browsers won't cache it, so it needs our \n    service every single time.\n    -> Good for Analystic in server and make \n    sure that the server works, as it hots server\n    everytime.\n\nSince we dont care about Analystics,\n302 makes more sense here...\n\n2. 301 Redirect:\n    -> A Permanent Redirect. Browser \n    knows where to redirect, and it won't\n    need our service anymore.\n    -> Good, if want to save the overhead\n    compute of lookingup the long url for \n    the short one.\n    -> Efficient but one-time use-case only !",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
